 Break Points    	Class     Dimensions    Target
Extra small        (none)       <567 px     (Mobile Phones)
Small                sm         >=576 px    (Tablets)
Medium               md         >=786 px    (old monitor and small laptop)
Large                lg         >=992 px    (Laptop)
Extra Large          xl 	    >=1200 px   (Desktop)
Extra Extra Large    xxl        >=1400 px   (Flatscreen TV)